title: Vacationing with Kids is NOT a Vacation
description: Falen's back from vacation and learned something new about what it's like to vacation with a baby, Mixtape Game, COVID-19 Stories, the listener that we've been talking to about the letter he got from his dad is back for another update, Dave' daughter Alison joins the show for Baby Price is Right,  Cousin Skeeter Bonsett reads us a bedtime story, and more!
